    "description": "KYC/KYB identity verification and short-lived auth token issuance for the Meridian platform.\n\n## Purpose\n\nDocumentation collection — the consumer-facing surface.\n\n## Getting started\n\nObtain OAuth 2.0 client credentials from the Meridian developer portal, then exchange for an access token. See `Authentication` for full detail.\n\n## Consumers\n\n- External integrators\n- Solutions engineering\n\n## Conventions\n\n- Every folder maps 1:1 to a resource\n- Every request has rich markdown documentation",
